ActBalanced Refugee Reform Act
SubjectOrder Fixing December 15, 2012 as the Day on which Certain Sections of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing December 15, 2012 as the day on which sections 1, 7, 10 to 12, 14.1, 17 to 23 and 26, subsection 27(2) and sections 29, 30, 33 to 35, 37 and 41 of the BALANCED REFUGEE REFORM ACT, chapter 8 of the Statutes of Canada, 2010, COME INTO FORCE.
